      <title>拉加德预计通胀率将进一步下降，但寻求回归 2% 的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/lagarde-sees-more-disinflation-but-seeks-proof-of-return-to-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长拉加德表示，欧元区通胀回落将继续，但她和同事需要看到更多证据表明物价增长正在回归目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/lagarde-sees-more-disinflation-but-seeks-proof-of-return-to-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:12:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
