    <item>
      <title>Cathie Wood 减少了对 Nvidia 的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-26/cathie-wood-reduces-exposure-to-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cathie Wood 两年多以来首次出售了台湾积体电路制造公司 (Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Corp.) 的股票，进一步削减了该芯片制造商主要客户英伟达 (Nvidia) 的风险敞口。凯蒂·格雷菲尔德报道“彭博公开赛”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-26/cathie-wood-reduces-exposure-to-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 15:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀担忧困扰战时经济 以色列暂停降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/israel-pauses-rate-cuts-as-inflation-worries-stalk-war-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列央行维持利率不变，选择不连续第二次降息，因为担心随着针对哈马斯的战争继续进行，通货膨胀可能会再次加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/israel-pauses-rate-cuts-as-inflation-worries-stalk-war-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗聘请摩根大通的 Raghavan 担任银行业务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/citigroup-hires-vis-raghavan-from-jpmorgan-as-head-of-banking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团聘请了摩根大通公司Co. 的 Viswas Raghavan 领导其新成立的银行部门，首席执行官 Jane Fraser 正在推进该银行数十年来最大规模的重组，而他是从一个主要竞争对手那里挖来的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/citigroup-hires-vis-raghavan-from-jpmorgan-as-head-of-banking</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:03:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
